{"tid":1976134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［又一單］碧藍幻想活動發生天朝玻璃事件，台灣人又打到人成地玻璃碎片","createTime":"2020-04-17T04:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T13:44:27.000Z","uid":10717,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1df1ec860f835d98baba657c2f60a1f301b99904","tid":1976134,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"這是這幾天天朝玻璃事件的其中之一，由來大概是一個中國騎空團對到台灣團，台灣團大幅度領先後把團名改成&ldquo;中國武漢肺炎&rdquo;，想當然，中國方大怒然後截圖發到 NGA （中國大型綜合遊戲論壇）結果  NGA 論壇怕惹事上身，開始刪文，於是粉紅們生氣了，覺得為什麼不給發。好巧不巧台灣團了解情況後表示  NGA 版主 484 其實是台灣的內鬼啊，所以才刪文不給發。<br />\n<br />\n然後粉紅居然信了，因為在他們的認知中「牆是雙向的」一定有內鬼，台灣人才會這麼快知道情報。於是就開始了一場自己人打自己人的戰爭，最後搞的 NGA 一度全站禁止留言。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑的是島民們還唯恐不亂的繼續反串wwww<br />\n<br />\n其他的玻璃事件還有 Nnevvy、兔田等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNCZZPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNCZZPY.jpg&h=e3305c92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNAdjPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNAdjPZ.jpg&h=a6cd14a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RS5s8Jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRS5s8Jj.jpg&h=bd626297&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xaRPCBF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxaRPCBF.jpg&h=9d085f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BBzOJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BBzOJw.jpg&h=809a7e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nwcAo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nwcAo9.jpg&h=87d8f1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571191bd7d895dd2bde89cea9174b8c9a1b3135a","tid":1976134,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"